<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: url('/background%20image.jpg') no-repeat center center fixed;
            background-size: cover;
        }
        .navbar {
            background-color: #FF8C00;
            padding: 10px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center; /* Center items */
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px; /* Space between navbar and content */
        }
        .navbar a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 15px; /* Padding around the links */
            font-size: 18px;
            margin: 0 10px; /* Space between links */
            border-radius: 5px; /* Rounded corners */
            transition: background-color 0.3s; /* Smooth transition */
        }
        .navbar a:hover {
            background-color: darkorange; /* Change color on hover */
        }
        .content {
            position: relative;
            color: orange;
            z-index: 2;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            margin-top: 20%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
        <a href="/admin-login">Admin Login</a>
        <a href="/verifier-login">Verifier Login</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="content">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <p>We are a team of developers passionate about decentralized technologies and blockchain-based solutions.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
